OL,3,CInquest opened into death of boy, 2,
OL,4,Cwho fell into the River Soar in
OL,5,CLeicester
OL,7,FThe parents of a two-year-old boy who
OL,8,Ffell into the River Soar in Leicester
OL,9,Fsay he "will be missed, and will
OL,10,Falways be loved."
OL,12,FAn inquest has been opened today into
OL,13,Fthe death of Xielo Maruziva, who went
OL,14,Fmissing after going into the water in
OL,15,Fthe Aylestone Meadows nature reserve,
OL,16,Fclose to Marsden Lane in February 2024.
OL,18,FHis body was found nearly four months
OL,19,Flater in the area after specialist
OL,20,Fsearches were carried out.
