OL,7,FAt the inquest, a jury has heard
OL,8,Ftributes to the boy from his mother,
OL,9,FKayela Smith.
OL,11,FShe described him as having "the
OL,12,Fbiggest personality for such a small
OL,13,Flittle boy".
OL,15,FMs Smith added: "He was full of
OL,16,Flaughter, he meant everything to me,
OL,17,Fhe was my best friend."
