OL,5,CLeicester
OL,7,FSenior coroner Professor Catherine
OL,8,FMason reminded the jury how on Sunday
OL,9,F18th Feburary 2024 Xielo was walking
OL,10,Fnear the canal with his aunts.
OL,12,FShe told them he walked away and then
OL,13,Fdisappeared from view. His body was
OL,14,Fthen found, not far from where he
OL,15,Fdisappeared on June 6th.
OL,17,FDI Haines from Leicestershire Police
OL,18,Falso gave evidence at today's hearing.
