OL,7,FHe was the senior investigating
OL,8,Fofficer whose role was to examine the
OL,9,Fcircumstances of how Xielo fell into
OL,10,Fthe water.
OL,12,FHe told the inquest there "wasn't a
OL,13,Flot" of CCTV, but they were able to
OL,14,Fgather "snapshots" of the toddler
OL,15,Fwalking.
OL,17,FHe confirmed that Xielo entered the
OL,18,Fwater at 5pm on the 18th February,
OL,19,Fwhen police received multiple calls.
