OL,7,FDI Haines also spoke about not knowing
OL,8,Fthe area is in a flood plain, saying:
OL,9,F"The area looked very different on
OL,10,FMonday compared to the previous day
OL,11,Fdue to high water levels."
OL,13,FThe inquest also heard from
OL,14,FPathologist Dr Frances Hollingbury,
OL,15,Fwho carried out a post mortem
OL,16,Fexamination on Xielo.
OL,18,FShe told the jury: "Xielo was staying
OL,19,Fat his dad's house, as he would most
OL,20,Fweekends and had been out for a walk
OL,21,Fwith his two aunts.
