OL,7,F"They were walking in the direction of
OL,8,FPackhorse Bridge. She was told about
OL,9,Fan extensive search for him."
OL,11,FShe said he died from the effects of
OL,12,Fbeing immersed in water, and that she
OL,13,Fcouldn't ignore the fact he fell into
OL,14,Fcold water.
OL,16,FAsked by the coroner if there had been
OL,17,Fa swift loss of consciousness, she
OL,18,Freplied "yes that's correct" and added
OL,19,Fthat "once he was unconscious, he
OL,20,Fwouldn't be aware of what was
OL,21,Fhappening".
